    			</language>
    			<translation>
    				Anti-astrologer. [See] above.
    			</translation>
    		</marginalia>
    		<marginalia hand="Italian">
    			<language ident="LA">
    				<position place="intext" book_orientation="180">
    					<marginalia_text>
    						Alij pauci optim&egrave;: tu melius.
    					</marginalia_text>
    					<emphasis method="chalk" type="straight"/>
    				</position>
    			</language>
    			<translation>
    				A few other men are great: you are better.
    			</translation>
    		</marginalia>
    		<marginalia hand="Italian">
    			<language ident="LA">
    				<position place="tail" book_orientation="0">
    					<marginalia_text>
    						Fortij perpetua Meditatio. Quicquid
    						agis,
    					</marginalia_text>
    					<person name="Joachim Fortius Ringelberg"/>
    					<emphasis method="chalk" type="straight"/>
    				</position>
    			</language>
    			<language ident="IT">
    				<position place="tail" book_orientation="0">
    					<marginalia_text>
    						piu oltre.
    					</marginalia_text>
    					<emphasis method="chalk" type="straight"/>
    				</position>
    			</language>
    			<translation>
    				The continuous meditation of Fortius. Whatever you do, beyond that.
    			</translation>
    		</marginalia>
    		
    		
    		<marginalia hand="Italian">
    			<language ident="LA">
    				<position place="left_margin" book_orientation="90">
    					<marginalia_text>
    						Multi ben&egrave;: pauci meli&ugrave;s: rarissimi optim&egrave;: optimorum optim&egrave;, solus Eutrapelus.
    						Cui vnica verborum, rerum, actionu[m] pra[e]c[a]lentia: et singularis summaru[m] facultatu[m]
    						copia. Semper magis, magisq[ue] proficiens.		
    					</marginalia_text>
    					<person name="Eutrapelus"/>
    					<emphasis method="chalk" type="straight"/>
    				</position>
    			</language>
    			<translation>
    				Many men are well: few are better: even fewer are great: the best of the best is Eutrapelus alone,
    				who has a unique zeal for words, things, and actions, and a singular abundance of the highest faculties.
    				Always progressing more and more.
    			</translation>
    		</marginalia>
    		
    		<marginalia hand="Italian">
    			<language ident="LA">
    				<position place="right_margin" book_orientation="270">
    					<marginalia_text>
    						Quis, qualis, quantus? Ecquantum hoc in politicis, aut polemicis? Ecquid illud
    					</marginalia_text>
    					<emphasis method="chalk" type="straight"/>
    				</position>
    				<position place="tail" book_orientation="270">
    					<marginalia_text>
    						in magnis mundi negociationibus?
    					</marginalia_text>
    				</position>
    			</language>
    			<translation>
    				Who, of what kind, how much? This much in politics, or polemics? What is that in the great business of the world? <!--JG: Very unsure, esp. about ecquantum and ecquid-->
    			</translation>
    		</marginalia>
        
